# Component Structure Guide

This portfolio uses a component-based architecture with a modern, clean design approach:

## Section Components
These are the main portfolio sections:
- [src/components/Hero/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Hero/index.tsx) - Landing section with clean typography and subtle animations
- [src/components/About.tsx](mdc:src/components/About.tsx) - About section showcasing skills and background
- [src/components/Projects.tsx](mdc:src/components/Projects.tsx) - Projects showcase with minimalist card design
- [src/components/Experience.tsx](mdc:src/components/Experience.tsx) - Work experience with timeline layout
- [src/components/Contact.tsx](mdc:src/components/Contact.tsx) - Contact information with form

## Animation Components
These components handle animations throughout the site:
- [src/components/TextAnimation.tsx](mdc:src/components/TextAnimation.tsx) - Subtle text animations
- [src/components/ShapeAnimation.tsx](mdc:src/components/ShapeAnimation.tsx) - Minimalist shape animations
- [src/components/SwissMotion.tsx](mdc:src/components/SwissMotion.tsx) - Modern motion animations
- [src/components/ParallaxLayer.tsx](mdc:src/components/ParallaxLayer.tsx) - Subtle parallax effects

## Utility Components
- [src/components/SectionSkeleton.tsx](mdc:src/components/SectionSkeleton.tsx) - Base section structure
- [src/components/LazySection.tsx](mdc:src/components/LazySection.tsx) - Lazy loading sections
- [src/components/ScrollIndicator.tsx](mdc:src/components/ScrollIndicator.tsx) - Modern scroll indicator
- [src/components/ClientLayout.tsx](mdc:src/components/ClientLayout.tsx) - Handles client-side layout effects

## Navigation/Layout
- [src/components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.tsx) - Clean navigation with mobile responsiveness
- [src/components/Footer.tsx](mdc:src/components/Footer.tsx) - Minimal footer with essential links

## Section-Specific Components
Each main section may have its own sub-components:
- Hero: [src/components/Hero/index.tsx](mdc:src/components/Hero/index.tsx)
- About: [src/components/About/types.ts](mdc:src/components/About/types.ts)
- Projects: [src/components/Projects/](mdc:src/components/Projects)
- Experience: [src/components/Experience/](mdc:src/components/Experience)
- Contact: [src/components/Contact/](mdc:src/components/Contact)
